author: @mvnsasvwvnt_06
text: Remember guys, not every good song is a title track, all songs in this album r ridiculously good. An album is like story telling, the songs should be placed well. IVE Empathy is one of the best albums made, all the songs r kept in the right place. Try and go into depth of what the album is telling, u will not be dissapointed. IVE never fails to provide artistically beautiful albums. They don't just make 'catchy' music as many ppl believe. They go into depth with their music, I hope ppl focus on the topics they share through music instead of focusing on the stupidest things known to mankind. These 6 girls will surely make it really big one day, their producers, song writers and staffs also did a great job with this album
